<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1048066' id='t-1048066'>And so looking to the future,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1049995' id='t-1049995'>it's going to be
really exciting to explore</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1052032' id='t-1052032'>what this can tell us about the world.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:45
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1054381' id='t-1054381'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
